## Added a collapsing view to messages to keep UI cleaner.
#### Behaviour:
Read more button appears when message length goes beyond certain number of chars.
This length can be modified in Constants.jsx

Link - http://theshubham99.github.io/AdventureSite

This will be consistent across all kinds of messages. (from user & gooey) and a separate component can be built if needed in the future.

@pollend @smsunarto  @majordwarf
